this api returns the entries relating to an account for a certain period in a certain year  
In the rest you must enter the account, the year and the period.

The period is obtained from the following api

[https://rest.reviso.com/accounts/2310/accounting-years/2022/periods](https://rest.reviso.com/accounts/2310/accounting-years/2022/periods)

