[https://rest.reviso.com/vat-accounts/A303](https://rest.reviso.com/vat-accounts/A303)

It's necessary to insert the **vatCode** on the rest and modify the raw in the body.

For example:

``` json
{
    "account": {
        "accountNumber": 2720005
    },
    "exemptVatCode": {
        "code": "N3.6"
    },
    "isTotalVatAccountIncluded": false,
    "name": "Acquisti N.I. art. 74 ter agenzie di viaggio",
    "ratePercentage": 0.00000000,
    "vatReportSetup": {
        "vatReportSetupNumber": 12201
    },
    "vatType": {
        "name": "Purchases VAT",
        "vatTypeNumber": 2
    },
    "includesStampDuty": false,
    "vatCode": "A303"
}

```

The json response is:

``` json
{
    "account": {
        "accountNumber": 2720005,
        "self": "https://rest.reviso.com/accounts/2720005"
    },
    "exemptVatCode": {
        "code": "N3.6",
        "self": "https://rest.reviso.com/exempt-vat-codes/N3_11_6"
    },
    "isTotalVatAccountIncluded": false,
    "name": "Acquisti N.I. art. 74 ter agenzie di viaggio",
    "ratePercentage": 0.00000000,
    "vatReportSetup": {
        "vatReportSetupNumber": 12201,
        "self": "https://rest.reviso.com/vat-types/2/vat-report-setups/12201"
    },
    "vatType": {
        "name": "Purchases VAT",
        "vatTypeNumber": 2,
        "self": "https://rest.reviso.com/vat-types/2"
    },
    "includesStampDuty": false,
    "vatCode": "A303",
    "self": "https://rest.reviso.com/vat-accounts/A303"
}

```

